title: Jada Bower’s CV
text:
Computer Scientist and Mathematician.

jadabower@gmail.com | Linkedin



Majoring in Computer Science with a Minor in Mathematics at Brigham Young University-Idaho. I am in my junior year and will graduate at the end of the year.


Full-stack development, Calculus, Machine Learning.




2022-present Brigham Young University-Idaho, Rexburg



2024 Retail Architects, South Carolina

Created full Vue.js mini-applications
Formatted documents/customer receipts with HTML and CSS
Used Google Cloud Run Functions with API calls to create an automated messaging system between GitHub and Freshdesk

2024 Observatory Operator, Brigham Young University-Idaho

Operated Celestron telescope and observaory dome
Provided interesting space facts for guests

2024 Programming with Classes TA, Brigham Young University-Idaho

Graded assignments
Helped students one-on-one to understand the fundamentals of Object-Oriented Programming

2023 Electrical Engineering TA, Brigham Young University-Idaho

Graded assignments
Helped students on in-class lab assignments
